        <text>
            <body>  <p>Ego <persName key="d1e11551" xml:id="d1e130023">Martinus, archidiaconus
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#322865" xml:id="d1e130025">Flaviniaci</placeName>
                        </persName>, notum facio omnibus presentes litteras inspecturis <lb n="2"/>
                        quod cum <persName key="d1e11557" xml:id="d1e130030">Renerius, miles de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324439" xml:id="d1e130032">Darceio</placeName>
                        </persName>, coram me traheret in causam fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e130035">Fontenetenses</orgName>
                        <lb n="3"/> super campo qui dicitur <q>
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325112" xml:id="d1e130040">de Fossa</placeName>
                        </q> et quibusdam aliis possessionibus, idem Fontenetenses res<lb n="4" break="no"/>ponderunt se per triginta annos et amplius res petitas
                        legitime possedisse et honus <lb n="5"/> hujusmodi probationis sibi
                        assumpserunt. Die autem ad hoc assignata exhibuerunt <lb n="6"/>
                        instrumentum <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324645" xml:id="d1e130050">venerabilis
                            patris Stephani <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e130052">Eduensis</placeName> episcopi</persName> per quod evidenter patuit
                        ipsos <lb n="7"/> res deductas in judicium datas in elemosinam de laude et
                        assensu dicti militis <lb n="8"/> per triginta et novem annos possedisse.
                        Tandem auditis ab utraque parte propositis, ser<lb n="9" break="no"/>vato
                        juris ordine de prudentium virorum consilio, dictos fratres ab impe<subst>
                            <del>d</del>
                            <add>ti</add>
                        </subst>tione <lb n="10"/> dicti militis per diffinitivam sententiam absolvi
                        eidem super premissis perpetuum silen<lb n="11" break="no"/>tium imponendo.
                        In cujus rei testimonium presenti scripto sigilli mei apposui fir<lb n="12" break="no"/>mamentum. Actum anno gratie milesimo ducentesimo
                        terciodecimo.</p>
                
            </body>
